                <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.T.1.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 64</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian"
                        notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00"
                        >undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>Addition to Article 64 of the Peace treaty with Italy: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“The basis for calculation for the payment of indemnity will be the
                            United States dollar, at its gold parity on the day of the signing of
                            the Peace treaty, i.e. 35 dollars for one ounce of gold.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
